column16: Colby Rasmus grounds into a double play, shortstop J.   Hardy to first baseman Mark Reynolds.   Anthony Gose out at 2nd.
Brett Lawrie flies out to right fielder Chris Davis.
Anthony Gose singles on a fly ball to center fielder Adam Jones.  P.   Arencibia to 2nd.
Danny Valencia flies out to right fielder Lew Ford.
Ryan Lavarnway flies out to center fielder Adam Jones.
